@startuml building_block_view
title Building Block View - Zalo Clone Internal Components (Simplified)

!theme plain

package "Frontend Layer" {
    [Web Application\n(React)]
    [Mobile Application\n(React Native)]
}

package "Backend Services" {
    [Authentication\nService]
    [User Management\nService]
    [Chat & Messaging\nService]
    [File Upload\nService]
}

database "User Database\n(PostgreSQL)" as userDB
database "Chat Database\n(MongoDB)" as chatDB
database "Cache\n(Redis)" as cache

cloud "Google Cloud Storage" as storage

[Web Application\n(React)] --> [Authentication\nService] : Login/Register
[Web Application\n(React)] --> [User Management\nService] : Manage profile,\nfriends
[Web Application\n(React)] --> [Chat & Messaging\nService] : Send/receive\nmessages
[Web Application\n(React)] --> [File Upload\nService] : Upload images,\nvideos

[Mobile Application\n(React Native)] --> [Authentication\nService] : Login/Register
[Mobile Application\n(React Native)] --> [User Management\nService] : Manage profile,\nfriends
[Mobile Application\n(React Native)] --> [Chat & Messaging\nService] : Send/receive\nmessages
[Mobile Application\n(React Native)] --> [File Upload\nService] : Upload images,\nvideos

[Authentication\nService] --> userDB : Store user\ncredentials
[Authentication\nService] --> cache : Store sessions

[User Management\nService] --> userDB : User profiles,\nfriendships

[Chat & Messaging\nService] --> chatDB : Store messages
[Chat & Messaging\nService] --> cache : Online status,\ntyping indicators

[File Upload\nService] --> storage : Store files

note bottom of "Backend Services"
  All services built with Node.js
  Use REST API + WebSocket
  Deployed on Google Cloud Platform
end note

note top of "Frontend Layer"
  **Web**: React.js for browsers
  **Mobile**: React Native for iOS/Android
  Shared code and API integration
end note

note bottom of storage
  Google Cloud Storage
  for media files
end note

@enduml